  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Free treatment for Children with Thalassemia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We are raising funds to provide free treatment to children effected from thalassemia and generate public awareness for the treatment and prevention of this disease. We have established a Thalassemia Unit and a Blood Bank for the free treatment of children affected by this disease. Thalassemia is a fairly expensive disease to treat. Since the patients often fall under the lower income group category, therefore, its treatment poses huge financial threats and psychological stress on them.</narrative>
  </description>
